	* tools/include/svp/testoutput.h: Output using `unsigned
	char'. (saves one instruction on Alpha)

2010-02-09  Raphael 'kena' Poss  <r.c.poss@uva.nl>

	Extend and improve the SL standard library.

	* lib/include/cassert.h,
