	`dtoa'/`strtod', etc.
	* lib/gdtoa.mk: New.

	* lib/src/dtoa_simple.c: Provide alternative `dtoa' since the
	gdtoa code seems to have FP issues on the MG simulator at this
	point.

	* lib/src/floatio.h,
	* lib/src/fpmath.h,
	* lib/src/_hdtoa.c,
	* lib/src/fprintf.c,
	* lib/src/perror.c,
