2010-01-24  Raphael 'kena' Poss  <r.c.poss@uva.nl>

	Upgrade COMA support to latest simulator changes (+ bug fixes).

	* tools/lib/mt-profiles/coma128,
	* tools/lib/mt-profiles/coma256,
	* tools/lib/mt-profiles/ml-npcrypt-p1,
